INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('great_war', 'The Great War, also known as the First War Against the Empire by the Thalmor, was a significant conflict that occurred from 4E 171 to 175 between the Third Empire and the Third Aldmeri Dominion. The war began with a Thalmor invasion of Imperial territory, motivated by the desire to assert dominance following the destabilization of Summerset after the Oblivion Crisis. The Thalmor seized control of the Summerset Isles in 4E 22 and later annexed Valenwood and Elsweyr, further consolidating their power.

The conflict escalated after the Thalmor demanded tributes, territorial concessions, and the disbandment of the Blades, along with a ban on the worship of Talos. When the Emperor rejected these demands, the Thalmor initiated hostilities, leading to the capture of the Imperial City. Although the Empire managed to reclaim the city, the war ended with the signing of the White-Gold Concordat, a peace treaty that imposed harsh terms on the Empire, including the suppression of Talos worship and the cession of large portions of southern Hammerfell. This war marked a pivotal moment in Tamriel''s history, highlighting the decline of Imperial power and the rise of the Aldmeri Dominion.', '''171'':26B ''175'':28B ''22'':74B ''4e'':25B,73B ''after'':60B,88B ''against'':12B ''aldmeri'':36B,194B ''along'':101B ''also'':6B ''although'':128B ''and'':33B,75B,79B,95B,164B,189B ''annex'':77B ''as'':8B ''assert'':53B ''ban'':104B ''beg'':40B ''betw'':29B ''blad'':100B ''by'':15B,49B ''captur'':123B ''cession'':166B ''city'':127B,135B ''concessions'':94B ''concordat'':147B ''conflict'':21B,86B ''consolidating'':82B ''control'':67B ''crisis'':63B ''declin'':185B ''demand'':91B ''demands'':115B ''desir'':51B ''destabilization'':57B ''disbandment'':97B ''dominanc'':54B ''dominion'':37B,195B ''elsweyr'':80B ''emperor'':112B ''empir'':14B,32B,130B,157B ''ended'':138B ''escalat'':87B ''first'':10B ''following'':55B ''from'':24B ''furth'':81B ''gold'':146B ''great'':1A,4B ''hammerfell'':172B ''harsh'':153B ''highlighting'':183B ''history'':182B ''hostiliti'':119B ''imperial'':46B,126B,187B ''impos'':152B ''in'':72B,179B ''including'':158B ''initiat'':118B ''invasion'':44B ''isles'':71B ''known'':7B ''larg'':168B ''lat'':76B ''leading'':120B ''manag'':131B ''mark'':175B ''moment'':178B ''motivat'':48B ''oblivion'':62B ''occurr'':23B ''of'':45B,58B,68B,98B,108B,124B,142B,161B,167B,170B,186B,192B ''on'':105B,155B ''peac'':149B ''pivotal'':177B ''portions'':169B ''pow'':84B,188B ''reclaim'':133B '