INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('eternal_champion', 'The Eternal Champion, reputedly known as Talin, emerged as a pivotal hero in Tamriel''s history during the late Third Era. Born in 3E 370, he is best remembered for his critical role in ending the Imperial Simulacrum in 3E 399. The Eternal Champion successfully gathered the fragments of the Staff of Chaos, a powerful artifact, which enabled him to confront and defeat the impostor emperor, Jagar Tharn. His quest culminated in the rescue of the true emperor, Uriel Septim VII, alongside General Talin Warhaft, who had been imprisoned in a realm of Tharn''s choosing for a decade. This heroic act not only restored the rightful leadership of the Empire but also ended Tharn''s deceptive reign.', '''370'':27B ''399'':43B ''3e'':26B,42B ''act'':104B ''alongsid'':84B ''also'':115B ''and'':64B ''artifact'':58B ''as'':8B,11B ''been'':90B ''best'':30B ''born'':24B ''but'':114B ''cha'':55B ''champion'':2A,5B,46B ''choosing'':98B ''confront'':63B ''critical'':34B ''culminat'':73B ''decad'':101B ''deceptiv'':119B ''defeat'':65B ''during'':19B ''emerg'':10B ''emperor'':68B,80B ''empir'':113B ''enabl'':60B ''ended'':116B ''ending'':37B ''eternal'':1A,4B,45B ''for'':32B,99B ''fragments'':50B ''gather'':48B ''general'':85B ''had'':89B ''her'':14B ''heroic'':103B ''him'':61B ''his'':33B,71B ''history'':18B ''imperial'':39B ''impostor'':67B ''imprison'':91B ''in'':15B,25B,36B,41B,74B,92B ''is'':29B ''jag'':69B ''known'':7B ''lat'':21B ''leadership'':110B ''not'':105B ''of'':51B,54B,77B,95B,111B ''only'':106B ''pivotal'':13B ''powerful'':57B ''quest'':72B ''realm'':94B ''reign'':120B ''remember'':31B ''reputedly'':6B ''rescu'':76B ''restor'':107B ''rightful'':109B ''rol'':35B ''s'':17B,97B,118B ''septim'':82B ''simulacrum'':40B ''staff'':53B ''successfully'':47B ''talin'':9B,86B ''tamriel'':16B ''tharn'':70B,96B,117B ''the'':3B,20B,38B,44B,49B,52B,66B,75B,78B,108B,112B ''third'':22B ''this'':102B ''to'':62B ''tru'':79B ''uriel'':81B ''v