INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('dawnbreaker', 'Dawnbreaker is a sacred Daedric artifact created by the Daedric Prince Meridia, known for its radiant power and effectiveness against the undead and other corrupt beings. This longsword features a unique crystal, the Dawnstar Gem, embedded in its cross-guard, emitting holy light. Forged to "burn away corruption and false life," Dawnbreaker is especially potent against Meridia''s enemies, such as undead, Daedra, and werewolves. When wielded, it deals magical or fire damage and has a chance to create a fiery explosion upon killing an undead enemy, which can harm other nearby undead and cause them to flee.', '''against'':21B,58B ''an'':87B ''and'':19B,24B,51B,66B,76B,96B ''artifact'':7B ''as'':63B ''away'':49B ''beings'':27B ''burn'':48B ''by'':9B ''can'':91B ''caus'':97B ''chanc'':79B ''corrupt'':26B ''corruption'':50B ''creat'':8B,81B ''cross'':41B ''cross-guard'':40B ''crystal'':33B ''daedr'':65B ''daedric'':6B,11B ''damag'':75B ''dawnbreak'':1A,2B,54B ''dawnst'':35B ''deals'':71B ''effectiveness'':20B ''embedd'':37B ''emitting'':43B ''enemi'':61B ''enemy'':89B ''especially'':56B ''explosion'':84B ''fals'':52B ''featur'':30B ''fiery'':83B ''fir'':74B ''fle'':100B ''for'':15B ''forg'':46B ''gem'':36B ''guard'':42B ''harm'':92B ''holy'':44B ''in'':38B ''is'':3B,55B ''it'':70B ''its'':16B,39B ''killing'':86B ''known'':14B ''lif'':53B ''light'':45B ''longsword'':29B ''magical'':72B ''meridi'':13B,59B ''nearby'':94B ''or'':73B ''other'':25B,93B ''potent'':57B ''pow'':18B ''princ'':12B ''radiant'':17B ''s'':60B ''sacr'':5B ''such'':62B ''the'':10B,22B,34B ''them'':98B ''this'':28B ''to'':47B,80B,99B ''unde'':23B,64B,88B,95B ''uniqu'':32B ''upon'':85B ''werewolv'':67B ''when'':68B ''which'':90B ''wield'':69B', 'daedric, daedra, scholar', 'Dawnbreaker is a sacred Daedric artifact created by the Daedric Prince Meridia, known for its radiant power and effectiveness against the undead and other corrupt beings.', '', '', 'artifac