INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('dragonsreach', 'Dragonsreach is a prominent location in the Cloud District of Whiterun, a central city in Skyrim. Situated atop three flights of stairs beginning at the Gildergreen tree, this iconic palace serves as the residence of the Jarl of Whiterun Hold, the seat of the hold’s political power, and the location of its jail. Overlooking the city and with the Throat of the World as its backdrop, Dragonsreach is divided into four main sections: the main hall, the Jarl’s Quarters, the Great Porch, and the dungeon.

The palace is steeped in history and legend, having been built around the remnants of a dragon trap purportedly used by Olaf One-Eye. Its interior is a hub of activity, centered around the Jarl’s throne, where courtiers and family members move about amidst ornate furnishings, grand feasts, and a roaring hearth. The court wizard’s laboratory and the Jarl’s personal quarters further enhance the palace''s grandeur, with treasures and artifacts scattered throughout.

Dragonsreach’s dungeon serves as Whiterun''s jail, featuring several cells, evidence storage, and an escape tunnel leading to the Guard Barracks. The Great Porch, once a dragon’s prison, now serves as a multipurpose area for guard training and hosting quests pivotal to Skyrim’s Civil War and main storyline. As a symbol of both Whiterun’s authority and its role in Skyrim’s tumultuous history, Dragonsreach stands as a monument to power, strategy, and lore.', '''about'':133B ''activity'':120B ''amidst'':134B ''an'':180B ''and'':50B,59B,86B,95B,129B,139B,148B,162B,179B,205B,214B,225B,241B ''are'':201B ''around'':100B,122B ''artifacts'':163B ''as'':33B,66B,170B,198B,217B,235B ''at'':25B ''atop'':19B ''authority'':224B ''backdrop'':68B ''barracks'':187B ''been'':98B ''beginning'':24B ''both'':221B ''built'':99B ''by'':109B ''cells'':176B ''center'':121B ''central'':14B ''city'':15B,58B ''civil'':212B ''cloud'':9B ''court'':144B ''courtiers'':128B ''district'':10B ''divid'':71B ''dragon'':105B,193B ''dragonsreach'':1A,2B,69B,166B,233B ''dungeon'':88B,168B ''enhanc'':155B ''escap'':181B ''evidenc'':177B ''eye'':113B ''family'':130B ''feasts'':138B ''featuring'':174B ''flights'':21B ''for'':202B ''four'':73B ''furnishings'':136B ''furth'':154B ''gildergr'':27B ''grand'':137B ''grandeur'':159B ''great'':84B,189B ''guard'':186B,203B ''hall'':78B ''having'':97B ''hearth'':142B ''history'':94B,232B ''hold'':41B,46B ''hosting'':206B ''hub'':118B ''iconic'':30B ''in'':7B,16B,93B,228B ''interior'':115B ''into'':72B ''is'':3B,70B,91B,116B ''its'':54B,67B,114B,226B ''jail'':55B,173B ''jarl'':38B,80B,124B,150B ''laboratory'':147B ''leading'':183B ''legend'':96B ''location'':6B,52B ''lor'':242B ''main'':74B,77B,215B ''members'':131B ''monument'':237B ''mov'':132B ''multipurpos'':200B ''now'':196B ''of'':11B,22B,36B,39B,44B,53B,63B,103B,119B,220B ''olaf'':110B ''once'':191B ''one'':112B ''one-ey'':111B ''ornat'':135B ''overlooking'':56B ''palac'':31B,90B,157B ''personal'':152B ''pivotal