INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('falkreath', 'Falkreath is a city in the south of Skyrim and serves as the capital of Falkreath Hold. Situated near the borders of Cyrodiil and Hammerfell, it was historically considered part of Cyrodiil but is now firmly within Skyrim''s boundaries. Governed by Jarl Siddgeir, Falkreath is initially aligned with the Empire, though its allegiance may shift during Skyrim''s civil war.

