INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('sadrith_mora', 'Sadrith Mora, meaning "Mushroom Forest" in Dark Elvish, was the seat of power for Great House Telvanni on the island of Vvardenfell. Situated on an island in the Zafirbel Bay, it was accessible primarily by boat or teleportation, and entry required a certification of hospitality. Dominated by Tel Naga, the central Telvanni tower and home of the local councilor, Sadrith Mora was characterized by its mushroom-inspired architecture, sprawling markets, and strict governance by House Telvanni. The city also hosted the Telvanni Council House and Wolverine Hall, an Imperial bastion incongruously located in Telvanni territory. Known for its exclusive culture, the city exemplified Telvanni independence and disdain for outside influence.

