INSERT INTO public.oghma VALUES ('anvil', 'Anvil, located on the Gold Coast by the Abecean Sea, is a prominent harbor city and the seat of County Anvil in southwestern Cyrodiil. Known for its Redguard-influenced architecture and bustling maritime trade, Anvil features notable districts such as Castle Anvil, Chapelgate, and Harborside. The city''s landmarks include the Chapel of Dibella, the mysterious Mermaid Statue, and Benirus Manor, which carries a dark history of necromancy. Anvil also hosts the Fighters Guild and a Mages Guild chapter specializing in Restoration. Historically, the city served as a pirate haven before being transformed into a fortified settlement by King Bendu Olo, who led the All Flags Navy against the Sload in the First Era.

